message:
Update E2E tests for new CLI JSON output formats

- Update cli-auth.test.ts for new response schema:
  - login: { authenticated: true } instead of { success: true }
  - logout: { logged_out: true }
  - expired session: { error: true, code: "session_expired" }
- Add mobile bottom sheet drag-to-close test
- Tests pass with dev server running

Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.5 <noreply@anthropic.com>

